{"id":416867,"date":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":13}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"上海民歌选辑","genre":"","count":"89","ytitle":"","mtitle":"画朵葵花向太阳","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"师傅年老本姓张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满脸笑容走进赛诗场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天刚说文盲帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天镜副老花眼镜写诗章。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句写上毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一句写上共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有一句不会写，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画朵葵花向太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国染料三厂"}]}